title: AHS: 1984 Episode 2 Breakdown, Theories, and Details You Missed! | "Mr. Jingles"
author: Think Story
comment: Hot damn, this episode was hot, damn!. What do you guys think? Leave your comments and theories below and help me pray the boners away.
I cackled when Gus Kenworthy said “I can’t die with a guilty conscience, I did it. I took those steroids” and then Montana goes “WE FUCKING KNOW” 😂😂 Billie Lourd has the best delivery, I love her sm.
The over dramatic back story for Brooke is perfect
How do her glasses stay on if she is missing an ear?
I really didn’t expect to see ghost this season.
